The '''Truishii''' were a [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Realspace/Legends|space]]-traveling people that were known for their large caravans. A group of Truishii traders whose caravan was shipwrecked following a [[Hyperspace]] accident became the original colonists of [[Trevi IV]].<ref name="Fizzi">{{JournalCite|9|Fizzi's Slightly Used Starships (article)}}</ref>

